Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:16.94,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}从未示人的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:21.41,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}稍许流露而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:27.91,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}我已历经千磨百折
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:33.30,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}虽然我并不愿知晓这一切
